Package: libiosexec1
Name: libiosexec
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: iOS exec wrapper runtime library
 libiosexec provides wrappers for exec, posix_spawn, and related libc entry
 points so scripts and rootless account metadata behave consistently on iOS.
 .
 This package contains the runtime shared library.

Package: libiosexec-dev
Name: libiosexec (development files)
Architecture: any
Depends:
 libiosexec1 (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends}
Description: iOS exec wrapper runtime library (development files)
 This package contains the header, static archive, and development symlink
 needed to build software against libiosexec.
